      "content": "i get that but i feel like i'm overmedicated. my doctor is always so busy and i never really have time for all the extra appointments just for blood tests every little thing. if i've been stable on the 5mg for a long time and i'm eating the same way, wouldn't it be okay to just trial a lower dose like 2mg for a bit to see if my body handles it? it feels like a common sense thing if the symptoms aren't there.",
